message.de_DE: Unser Streben gilt allein der ultimativen Erfahrung.
message.ja_JP:
我々は究極の経験を
探し求めてきた。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/01]

message.en_US: However, just as we reached the creative freedom required to create it...

創造の自由をついに手にしたとき...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/01]
message.ko_KR: 창조하는 데 필요한 자유로운 환경이 조성되었지만...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/01]

message.en_US: With a heavy heart... we realized something else was amiss.

message.zh_CN: 我们沉重的发现...缺少了一样东西。<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/08/01]
